sum view cells: view of i32 gives i32:
  let total be 0
  for each index i of cells:
    total becomes total plus cells at i
  total

nested owned view gives i32:
  let total be 0
  for i from 0 up to 3:
    let cells be owned buffer of 2 i32 filled with i
    total becomes total plus sum view cells
  total

main gives i32:
  nested owned view
